Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I've been using my Sharingan this whole time, plus four Raikiris...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to finish this quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're really good at combo attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Kakashi-sensei's Raikiri attack definitely connected!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is he not dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.23,0:03:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was sure I crushed his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what I actually killed was one of the masked monsters that came out of his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should assume that it died in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same when he dismantled my shuriken shadow mimic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like a heart was attached to his arm, and it moved independently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each of those monsters must have its own heart, along with his real one, and so they're all his.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, he has five hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can he-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although Kakashi-sensei's Raikiri took one down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we have to eliminate the four remaining hearts in order to kill him for good?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very sharp. You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each one contains a heart taken from a shinobi I've killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to stock back up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and your hearts will be perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By connecting his chakra circulatory system to multiple hearts, he changes his chakra's nature to that of the original owner's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder he can use so many types of nature manipulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,does Konoha bury their dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cuz if they do, it's gonna suck ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakuzu's gonna be all, "We have to dig up the bounty and take him to the exchange point!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fire-spitting bastard, I expected to get a little more mileage outta him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, he was worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Says the guy whose head he chopped off...
