Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If his attacks draw a single drop of blood from you, you're dead.
