Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've got a lot more experience than all of you put together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at your forehead protectors reminds me of the first Konoha shinobi I ever fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The First Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old is this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.94,0:18:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you really are immortal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's no such thing as true immortality in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just managed to extend my life by stealing the hearts of powerful shinobi I defeat before my current one gives out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not getting away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can only hold that shadow move for about five minutes before you run out of juice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now we're all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the best situation for me, you dipshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fire and wind masks are merging!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Including my own, I had five hearts total.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi, it's only fitting I take yours to replace the one you destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
